                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def3-242-18710227 t18710227-242-punishment-53"></join>Seven Years' Penal Servitude each</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">LOCKLAND</hi>—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18710227-242-punishment-54" type="punishmentDescription">
