                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-242-18710227 t18710227-242-punishment-54"></join>Eighteen Months' Imprisonment.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">THE COURT</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">ordered a reward of</hi> 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. <hi rend="italic">to be given to Mrs. Ballard.</hi>
